- Phase pipeline parallelism wiring, `ProgressCounter` exists
  from 5a3; the thread scheduler has to consult it between
  phases so phase N+1 starts as soon as N produces a morsel's
  worth.
- `classify_cores` signature should become `<const MAX_CORES: usize>`
